The all-in-one python scripts that generate the SCVT meshes using jigsaw method from Pedro Peixoto, this includes
the conversion of jigsaw vtk file to netcdf

see dicussion here:
https://forum.mmm.ucar.edu/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?f=12&t=291

and github repo here:
https://github.com/pedrospeixoto/MPAS-PXT/tree/master/grids/utilities/jigsaw

the python scripts here depend on
jigsaw-python/external/jigsaw/bin/jigsaw
